{
  "stem": "16571.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 525.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, then they-- they sort of-- they marched us out together.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Families joined up their women folk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were taken-- must have marched about three or four hours.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was ordinary-- what they had, they had these students who were training with make believe guns.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They looked like guns, but they were only made from wood.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we had about three Germans, and about half a dozen Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the rest were just civilian 18, 20-year-olds.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were sort of stretched out on this long, long queue of people which was six or seven villages.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we were marched to Viseu where we boarded a train all the way to-- didn't stop.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "All the way to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We didn't know then where we were going.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We-- we assumed we were going for labor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were in the ghetto for about four to five weeks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't exactly know how long.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Dragomiresti.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was called in Yiddish, it's Dragomiresti.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In Hungarian-- forget now which Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All-- all along.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All along.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We got on the train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was all the families.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anything from 150 people upwards.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were together with the families.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I remember afterwards thinking about it later on, that we-- my mother, they would hardly give us anything to eat for all these two, two and a half days we were traveling.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because they were saying, we don't know when we're going to be able to bake bread, when we be able to do some cooking.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they would rationing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They-- we had quite a lot of food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But they would-- they would-- they-- they reserved it for we don't know when we going to be able to bake and all the rest.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
